title: Refrigerator Water Filter - White
description: Refrigerator Water Filter - White ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 13 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11704498 Manufacturer Part Number EPTWFU01 This OEM refrigerator filter is for french door and side-by-side door types and is located in the back, top-right of your appliance. By absorbing heavy metals, pharmaceuticals, pesticides, chlorine, and much more, this filter provides delicious and healthy drinking water. This filter measures 2 inches deep, 9 inches high, 2 inches wide, and weighs 0.9 lbs. The installation is quick and easy with a push and twist feature. Don't forget to run water through the dispenser for about three minutes or 1.5 gallons to prepare the filter before use. For best performance replace this filter every six months.

installationInstructions.author: Claude from MARYVILLE, TN
installationInstructions.title: Change filter
installationInstructions.content: When removing existing filter you will experience some resistance at the 10-4 position which requires a little extra pressure to reach the 9-3 position.
